developers, dominating discussions in the tech industry. Companies are actively recruiting developers who possess a wide range of skills, capable of handling all aspects of web applications. With expertise spanning both front-end and back-end development, full-stack developers manage the entire web development process. This versatility makes them invaluable for creating seamless and integrated web solutions.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1693378998803\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q2. What is the salary of full stack web developer in India in 2023?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. The average salary for a full-stack developer in India stands at \u20b9375,000. Meanwhile, a full-stack developer with 1-4 years of experience can expect to earn a typical annual salary of \u20b9553,006.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1693379177478\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q3. What is the future of web dev?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans.  Pursuing a career in web development is a smart choice. The ever-changing technology landscape ensures a continuous demand for skilled web developers. This guarantees a promising and lasting career path in this field.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Web Developer Salary In 2024, web development is a fast-changing field in India. Businesses need to have a good online presence, so web developers are in high demand. Because of this, how much web developers earn is also changing. Understanding how much web developers make each month in India this year is important for people &#8230; <a title=\"Web Developer Salary In India 2024\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/web-developer-salary\/\" aria-label=\"More on Web Developer Salary In India 2024\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":5214,